Hello Tanuu, welcome to the technical interview for the Python internship position. I'm excited to learn more about your skills and experience with Python.

Before we begin, I want to outline the format of the interview. We'll be covering a range of topics, including Python fundamentals, data structures, and problem-solving. We'll also be discussing some real-world scenarios and how you would approach them using Python.

To make things more comfortable, I'll be asking you a mix of behavioral and technical questions. Don't worry if you need a moment to think before answering - it's completely fine.
